1. *Teoriju* je lako razumeti ako se posvetite proučavanju. (*Teoriju* - theory) (It is easy to understand *theory* if you dedicate yourself to studying.)

2. Ova knjiga razmatra *teoriju* relativnosti Alberta Ajnštajna. (*Teoriju* - theory) (This book discusses *Einstein's theory* of relativity.)

3. Ona nije prihvatila *teoriju* da je zemlja ravna ploča. (*Teoriju* - theory) (She didn't accept the *theory* that the Earth is flat.)

4. Doktorat iz sociologije je zahtevao temeljito razumevanje društvenih *teorija*. (društvenih *teorija* - social theories) (A PhD in sociology required a thorough understanding of social *theories*.)

5. *Teoriju* muzike možete naučiti u muzičkoj školi. (*Teoriju* - music theory) (You can learn *music theory* at a music school.)

6. On je kritikovao *teoriju* evolucije Čarlsa Darvina. (*Teoriju* - theory) (He criticized *Charles Darwin's theory* of evolution.)

7. Bez obzira na *teoriju* zavere, vakcine su važne za zaštitu zdravlja. (*Teoriju* zavere - conspiracy theory) (Regardless of the *conspiracy theory*, vaccines are important for protecting health.)

8. Nije lako primeniti *teoriju* na praksu. (*Teoriju* - theory) (It's not easy to apply *theory* to practice.)

9. *Teoriju* otklona možete primeniti za procenu kvaliteta rezultata merenja. (*Teoriju* otklona - deviation theory) (You can apply *deviation theory* to assess the quality of measurement results.)

10. *Teoriju* relativiteta nije lako razumeti bez poznavanja matematike. (*Teoriju* relativiteta - theory of relativity) (It's not easy to understand the *theory of relativity* without knowledge of mathematics.)